00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:39.440
as vice-president as part of
his duties for Dwight Eisenhower

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:41.880
and that he had learned a great
deal and impressed a lot of people.

00:05:41.880 --> 00:05:44.920
He seemed to have really
taken that on as a study

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:46.590
through much of the
rest of his life.

00:05:46.590 --> 00:05:48.720
But one of the things about the
