00:05:55.300 --> 00:05:58.650
to fight but Richard Nixon found us
fighting when he became president

00:05:58.650 --> 00:06:03.850
in Vietnam, of course, and the
news that you broke had to do

00:06:03.850 --> 00:06:06.860
with a person named Anna Chennault.

00:06:06.860 --> 00:06:10.420
Famous to perhaps our generation
and the generation before us,

00:06:10.420 --> 00:06:14.140
but not so well known today who
was sent on a mission by the,

00:06:14.140 --> 00:06:16.140
if you will, Nixon White House

00:06:16.140 --> 00:06:18.610
in waiting before he
was elected president;

00:06:18.610 --> 00:06:20.300
when he was still a private citizen

00:06:20.300 --> 00:06:21.840
but the nominee of
the Republican party.

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:23.800
What was that all about?

00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:25.960
&gt;&gt; John Farrell: Well,
it's almost 50 years.

00:06:25.960 --> 00:06:28.450
It'll be 50 years next year.

00:06:28.450 --> 00:06:32.280
And Nixon was running in 1968.

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:35.150
An amazing year of turbulence.

00:06:35.150 --> 00:06:39.090 position:56%
The year that Bob Kennedy and Martin
Luther King were assassinated,

00:06:39.090 --> 00:06:43.420
and you had Eugene McCarthy
challenging LBJ in New Hampshire.

00:06:43.420 --> 00:06:46.400
You had riots at the
Democratic convention.

00:06:46.400 --> 00:06:48.760
And in the midst of all this,

00:06:48.760 --> 00:06:54.160 position:56%
Richard Nixon builds a pretty
formidable lead by September of 1968

00:06:54.160 --> 00:06:57.510
over his Democratic
opponent Hubert Humphrey

00:06:57.510 --> 00:07:00.000
because Lindon Johnson the
sitting president has announced

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:03.960
that he's not going to run for
reelection because of Vietnam.

00:07:03.960 --> 00:07:07.910
And then all of a sudden, the
Democratic party starts --

00:07:07.910 --> 00:07:12.450
the Democratic voters start
coming home in the fall of 1968.

00:07:12.450 --> 00:07:15.580
And the blue collar union
workers, they leave George Wallace

00:07:15.580 --> 00:07:17.310
who was running as a
third party candidate

00:07:17.310 --> 00:07:22.080
and they start going back
to the Democratic party.

00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:26.130
The Eugene McCarthy anti-war
