00:07:27.620 --> 00:07:32.800
of a tiptoe towards a
split with LBJ on Vietnam.

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:35.940
And all of a sudden what --
at the beginning of September,

00:07:35.940 --> 00:07:40.270
Richard Nixon had this young
guy who was a vote counter,

00:07:40.270 --> 00:07:43.600
and his name was Allen Greenspan.

00:07:43.600 --> 00:07:44.900
&gt;&gt; Ron Elving: Good counter.

00:07:44.900 --> 00:07:46.200
&gt;&gt; John Farrell: Yes.

00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:47.500
And Allen Greenspan
sends in a memo and says,

00:07:47.500 --> 00:07:49.390
"We're going to win
410 electoral votes.

00:07:49.390 --> 00:07:51.980
Humphrey will be lucky
if he wins a single state

00:07:51.980 --> 00:07:53.930 position:56%
because Wallace will take the rest."

00:07:53.930 --> 00:07:57.840
But it has closed dramatically
by the middle of September,

00:07:57.840 --> 00:08:01.630
and then Lindon Johnson
calls Nixon in and says,

00:08:01.630 --> 00:08:06.210
"We're seeing some
progress on Vietnam.

00:08:06.210 --> 00:08:10.170
I may institute a bombing halt."

00:08:10.170 --> 00:08:13.540
Now Richard Nixon thought that
he had lost the 1960 election

00:08:13.540 --> 00:08:17.740
because the Kennedy's stole it
from him, and he had seen Johnson

00:08:17.740 --> 00:08:23.700 position:56%
in 1966 do an October surprise in
the off-year congressional elections

00:08:23.700 --> 00:08:26.470
by announcing that he was
closer to peace in Vietnam.

00:08:26.470 --> 00:08:31.620
So Nixon's paranoia kicks in,
and he sees these forces lined

00:08:31.620 --> 00:08:36.320
up against him ready to steal
something from him once again,

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:39.410
and he uses this connection,
a woman named Anna Chennault

00:08:39.410 --> 00:08:42.570
who was very well-known
in the palaces of Asia

00:08:42.570 --> 00:08:46.790
because her husband Claire
Chennault had led the Flying Tigers

00:08:46.790 --> 00:08:53.850
into battle against the Japanese
in World War Two, and he sends her

00:08:53.850 --> 00:08:57.630
to the South Vietnamese to tell
them that if they can just hold

00:08:57.630 --> 00:09:00.460
on a little bit longer,
Nixon will be elected

00:09:00.460 --> 00:09:02.490
and you'll get a better deal.

00:09:02.490 --> 00:09:07.240
And so, rather than go to Paris
and join in the peace talks,

00:09:07.240 --> 00:09:11.850
which Nixon thinks is a charade,
the South Vietnamese resist.

00:09:11.850 --> 00:09:13.390
They don't join in the peace talks.

00:09:13.390 --> 00:09:17.860
Now this was pretty much a known
story because at some point

00:09:17.860 --> 00:09:21.670
that fall, Lyndon Johnson got
wind of it, and he sent the FBI

00:09:21.670 --> 00:09:26.110
