00:10:57.020 --> 00:10:59.600
to the South Vietnamese,"
and Nixon says, "No.

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:01.850
I would never do something
like that."

00:11:01.850 --> 00:11:05.380
So the last big piece of
the puzzle and the piece

00:11:05.380 --> 00:11:06.950
that confronted Lyndon Johnson

00:11:06.950 --> 00:11:12.070
